    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require installation and use of seatbelts on buses in Great Britain",
        "additional_details": "We want the Government to do this for the safety of passengers on the bus, bystanders and other users of transport on the roads. If they crash buses can be dangerous, and without seatbelts passengers can be hurt or even die.",
        "background": "We want the Government to introduce legislation to require seatbelts be installed on public buses in Great Britain, and make it mandatory for them to be used.",
